      <description>Q: What is the differances between the RiskyBOTs A: this is explained in this page, but in short they are do different features thus separate bot
Q: Riskybot 2 isn&amp;rsquo;t responding to me in chat A: Make sure that it has permissions to view in that channel - can&amp;rsquo;t see what doesn&amp;rsquo;t have permissions for
Q: Is the bot using any privileged intents A: The main bot is using no privileged intents, (but Riskybot 2 does use the message-content)</description>
